				"code": "| fromText toText change el |\nfromText := 'Texto original del snippet\nsegunda linea igual'.\ntoText := 'Texto modificado del snippet\nsegunda linea igual'.\nchange := GtDiffBuilder\n    computeDifferencesFrom: fromText\n    to: toText\n    using: GtCharacterGroupDiffSplitter words.\nel := GtDiffElement onChange: change.\nel aptitude: GtDiffFlatAptitude.\nel beSmallSize.\nel"
			},
