				"uid": {
					"__type": "uid",
					"uidString": "cLt4IEY1TF2Awoq4EQFnbw=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle": {
					"__type": "textStyle"
				},
				"string": "### Extensión IceNode: nueva pestaña \"Live Diff (two panes)\"\n\n`exampleIceNodeLiveDiffView` (iteración 4). Verificamos con BlScripter que el inspector de un `IceNode` de fichero `.lepiter` modificado muestra la pestaña \"Live Diff (two panes)\". La extensión `gtViewLiveTwoPanesDiffFor:` (categoría `*Lepiter-Literate-Diff`) añade la pestaña con priority 18 — justo antes que el `Diff (two panes)` existente (priority 19)."
			},
			{
				"__type": "pharoSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"code": "LpLtLiveDiffExamples compile: 'exampleIceNodeLiveDiffView\n    <gtExample>\n    <description: ''El inspector de un IceNode de fichero .lepiter muestra la pestaña Live Diff (two panes)''>\n    <return: #BlScripter>\n    <after: #cleanUpLepiterExamples>\n    | ex gtRepo diff iceNode pager scripter |\n    ex := GtIceLepiterExamples new.\n    gtRepo := ex gitRepositoryAEditExistingPage.\n    diff := gtRepo workingCopyDiff.\n    iceNode := diff tree children first children first children first.\n    pager := GtInspector createOn: iceNode.\n    scripter := BlScripter new element: pager.\n    scripter checkStep: [:s |\n        s label: ''Live Diff tab exists with correct title''.\n        s exists.\n        s // BrTab; @ [:tab | tab label asString = ''Live Diff (two panes)'']].\n    ^ scripter\n' classified: 'examples'."
			},
			{
				"__type": "textSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T20:45:40.996596+01:00"
					}
				},
				"paragraphStyle": {
					"__type": "textStyle"
				},
				"string": "**Exploración interactiva**\n\n`GtIceLepiterExamples` proporciona un repositorio Iceberg real con una página `.lepiter` modificada. La cadena `diff tree children first children first children first` recorre: nodo raíz → nodo base de datos → nodo páginas → nodo de la página concreta. Este `IceNode` tiene un `IceModification` cuya `key` termina en `.lepiter`."
			},
			{
				"__type": "pharoSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"code": "| repoName repo ex gtRepo diff iceNode |\n\"limpiar por si hay un repo registrado de una exploración anterior\"\nrepoName := GtIceLepiterExamples new repositoryName.\nrepo := IceRepository registry detect: [:r | r name = repoName] ifNone: [nil].\nrepo ifNotNil: [repo forget].\nex := GtIceLepiterExamples new.\ngtRepo := ex gitRepositoryAEditExistingPage.\ndiff := gtRepo workingCopyDiff.\niceNode := diff tree children first children first children first.\nex cleanUpRepositoriesAndDatabases.\n{ iceNode class name. iceNode value class name. iceNode value key }"
			},
			{
				"__type": "textSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"paragraphStyle": {
					"__type": "textStyle"
				},
				"string": "**Implementación mínima**\n\nEl método guarda `LpLtPageLiveDiffElement` con las dos condiciones de guarda: `value isKindOf: IceOperation` y `value key endsWith: '.lepiter'`. El método de cleanup `cleanUpLepiterExamples` delega a `GtIceLepiterExamples new cleanUpRepositoriesAndDatabases`."
			},
			{
				"__type": "pharoSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"createEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T09:58:08.843646+01:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T09:58:44.458765+01:00"
					}
				},
				"uid": {
					"__type": "uid",
					"uidString": "ErwBotSCQrisfBlYJC79vQ=="
				},
				"code": "IceNode compile: 'gtViewLiveTwoPanesDiffFor: aView\n    <gtView>\n    (self value isKindOf: IceOperation) ifFalse: [ ^ aView empty ].\n    ([self value key endsWith: ''.lepiter''] on: Error do: [:e | false]) ifFalse: [ ^ aView empty ].\n    ^ aView explicit\n        title: ''Live Diff (two panes)'';\n        priority: 18;\n        stencil: [\n            LpLtPageLiveDiffElement new\n                fromContents: self value rightContents;\n                toContents: self value leftContents ];\n        yourself\n' classified: '*Lepiter-Literate-Diff'."
			},
			{
				"__type": "pharoSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"code": "LpLtLiveDiffExamples compile: 'cleanUpLepiterExamples\n    GtIceLepiterExamples new cleanUpRepositoriesAndDatabases\n' classified: 'private - cleanup'."
			},
