				"createTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T10:18:56.432533+01:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T17:08:35.954216+01:00"
					}
				},
				"uid": {
					"__type": "uid",
					"uidString": "fKh1aOfYTEiBOADX4eqRWg=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle": {
					"__type": "textStyle"
				},
				"string": "### Fila `:modified` renderiza un `GtDiffElement`\n\nEl método `build` delega a `buildModified` cuando `status = #modified`. `buildModified` usa `GtDiffBuilder` para calcular el diff entre los textos de ambos snippets y lo pasa a un `GtDiffElement` con `GtDiffFlatAptitude`. El elemento recibe id `#diffElement` para que las aserciones de BlScripter puedan localizarlo. El sizing se hace con `constraintsDo:` — `BlElement` puro no responde a `hMatchParent`; esos métodos sólo existen en subclases que usan `BrLayoutResizerAptitude`. En esta iteración también se recompila `from:to:status:` para añadir la llamada a `build` — es aquí donde el primer ejemplo que verifica rendering lo requiere."
			},
			{
				"__type": "pharoSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"createEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T10:19:05.610968+01:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:03:40.362884+01:00"
					}
				},
				"uid": {
					"__type": "uid",
					"uidString": "uH8yv8wJQV+u0UcIAXu2Dg=="
				},
				"code": "LpLtLiveDiffExamples compile: 'exampleModifiedRowRendering\n    <gtExample>\n    <description: ''Fila :modified renderiza un GtDiffElement con id #diffElement''>\n    <return: #BlScripter>\n    | row scripter |\n    row := self exampleModifiedRow.\n    scripter := BlScripter new element: row.\n    scripter checkStep: [ :s |\n        s label: ''Modified row contains a GtDiffElement''.\n        s satisfies: [ :el | el isKindOf: GtDiffElement ].\n        s id: #diffElement ].\n    ^ scripter\n' classified: 'examples'."
			},
			{
				"__type": "textSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"createTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:03:56.216324+01:00"
					}
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:03:56.216324+01:00"
					}
				},
				"paragraphStyle": {
					"__type": "textStyle"
				},
				"string": "**Exploración interactiva**\n\nUn `GtDiffElement` construido con `GtDiffBuilder` y configurado con `aptitude: GtDiffFlatAptitude` es el elemento visual de diff inline. Verificamos que acepta `id:` y que el id queda accesible para BlScripter."
			},
			{
				"__type": "pharoSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"code": "| change diffEl |\nchange := GtDiffBuilder\n    computeDifferencesFrom: 'Texto original'\n    to: 'Texto modificado'\n    using: GtCharacterGroupDiffSplitter words.\ndiffEl := GtDiffElement onChange: change.\ndiffEl aptitude: GtDiffFlatAptitude.\ndiffEl beSmallSize.\ndiffEl id: #diffElement.\ndiffEl class name , ' - id: ' , diffEl id printString"
			},
			{
				"__type": "textSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"createTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:03:56.221215+01:00"
					}
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:03:56.221215+01:00"
					}
				},
				"paragraphStyle": {
					"__type": "textStyle"
				},
				"string": "**Implementación mínima**\n\n`snippetTextFor:` extrae el texto de cualquier subclase de snippet. `build` despacha por `status` — para `#modified` delega a `buildModified`, que construye el `GtDiffElement` con id `#diffElement`. `buildSingleSide` queda como stub para la siguiente iteración. En esta iteración también se recompila `from:to:status:` para añadir la llamada a `build` — es aquí donde el primer ejemplo que verifica rendering lo requiere."
			},
			{
				"__type": "pharoSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"createEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T10:20:08.18316+01:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:03:40.367109+01:00"
					}
				},
				"uid": {
					"__type": "uid",
					"uidString": "4y+CORyNSFiwM2Wg4yakOQ=="
				},
				"code": "LpLtSnippetDiffRowElement class compile: 'from: aFromSnippet to: aToSnippet status: aStatus\n    | row |\n    row := self new.\n    row pvtFromSnippet: aFromSnippet.\n    row pvtToSnippet: aToSnippet.\n    row pvtStatus: aStatus.\n    row build.\n    ^ row\n' classified: 'instance creation'.\n\nLpLtSnippetDiffRowElement compile: 'snippetTextFor: aSnippet\n    (aSnippet isKindOf: LeTextualSnippet) ifTrue: [ ^ aSnippet string ].\n    (aSnippet isKindOf: LeCodeSnippet) ifTrue: [ ^ aSnippet code ].\n    ^ aSnippet printString\n' classified: 'private'.\n\nLpLtSnippetDiffRowElement compile: 'build\n    self layout: BlLinearLayout horizontal.\n    self constraintsDo: [:c | c horizontal matchParent. c vertical fitContent].\n    status = #modified ifTrue: [ ^ self buildModified ].\n    self buildSingleSide\n' classified: 'building'.\n\nLpLtSnippetDiffRowElement compile: 'buildModified\n    | change diffEl |\n    change := GtDiffBuilder\n        computeDifferencesFrom: (self snippetTextFor: fromSnippet)\n        to: (self snippetTextFor: toSnippet)\n        using: GtCharacterGroupDiffSplitter words.\n    diffEl := GtDiffElement onChange: change.\n    diffEl aptitude: GtDiffFlatAptitude.\n    diffEl beSmallSize.\n    diffEl constraintsDo: [:c | c horizontal matchParent].\n    diffEl id: #diffElement.\n    self addChild: diffEl\n' classified: 'building'.\n\nLpLtSnippetDiffRowElement compile: 'buildSingleSide\n    \"Stub — implemented in next iteration\"\n' classified: 'building'."
			},
