				"paragraphStyle": {
					"__type": "textStyle"
				},
				"string": "### Filas `:added` y `:removed` tienen colores y paneles correctos\n\n`buildSingleSide` asigna el color de fondo según status (`Color r: 0.9 g: 1.0 b: 0.9` para `:added`, `Color r: 1.0 g: 0.9 b: 0.9` para `:removed`, gris muy claro para `:unchanged`) y construye dos paneles `#leftPanel` y `#rightPanel`. El panel del lado del snippet ausente queda vacío; el del lado presente contiene un `BrLabel` con el texto del snippet."
			},
			{
				"__type": "pharoSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"createEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T10:20:23.005053+01:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:07:30.038905+01:00"
					}
				},
				"uid": {
					"__type": "uid",
					"uidString": "hMbNJ9ruQliv7Sp6kbW68Q=="
				},
				"code": "LpLtLiveDiffExamples compile: 'exampleAddedRowRendering\n    <gtExample>\n    <description: ''Fila :added tiene fondo verde, panel izquierdo vacio y panel derecho con texto''>\n    <return: #BlScripter>\n    | row scripter |\n    row := self exampleAddedRow.\n    scripter := BlScripter new element: row.\n    scripter checkStep: [ :s |\n        s label: ''Added row has green background''.\n        s value: [ :el | el background paint color ]\n            equals: [ Color r: 0.9 g: 1.0 b: 0.9 ] ].\n    scripter checkStep: [ :s |\n        s label: ''Left panel is empty''.\n        s value: [ :el | el children size ] equals: [ 0 ].\n        s id: #leftPanel ].\n    scripter checkStep: [ :s |\n        s label: ''Right panel has one child''.\n        s value: [ :el | el children size ] equals: [ 1 ].\n        s id: #rightPanel ].\n    ^ scripter\n' classified: 'examples'.\n\nLpLtLiveDiffExamples compile: 'exampleRemovedRowRendering\n    <gtExample>\n    <description: ''Fila :removed tiene fondo rojo, panel izquierdo con texto y panel derecho vacio''>\n    <return: #BlScripter>\n    | row scripter |\n    row := self exampleRemovedRow.\n    scripter := BlScripter new element: row.\n    scripter checkStep: [ :s |\n        s label: ''Removed row has red background''.\n        s value: [ :el | el background paint color ]\n            equals: [ Color r: 1.0 g: 0.9 b: 0.9 ] ].\n    scripter checkStep: [ :s |\n        s label: ''Left panel has one child''.\n        s value: [ :el | el children size ] equals: [ 1 ].\n        s id: #leftPanel ].\n    scripter checkStep: [ :s |\n        s label: ''Right panel is empty''.\n        s value: [ :el | el children size ] equals: [ 0 ].\n        s id: #rightPanel ].\n    ^ scripter\n' classified: 'examples'."
			},
			{
				"__type": "textSnippet",
