				"paragraphStyle": {
					"__type": "textStyle"
				},
				"string": "### `LpLtPageLiveDiffElement` renderiza header, toolbar y lista de filas\n\n`buildDiff` ahora construye tres zonas además de calcular `diffRows`: un `#header` con dos `BrLabel` (\"Repository:\" y \"Working Copy (local):\"), un `#toolbar` con un `BrButton` que llama a `toggleUnchanged`, y un `#rowsPane` `BrVerticalPane` que contiene todas las filas. `showUnchanged` se inicializa a `true`."
			},
			{
				"__type": "pharoSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"createEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T10:20:49.876382+01:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:10:51.682713+01:00"
					}
				},
				"uid": {
					"__type": "uid",
					"uidString": "S9924szASHO2X8155tPUJQ=="
				},
				"code": "LpLtLiveDiffExamples compile: 'examplePageDiffRendering\n    <gtExample>\n    <description: ''LpLtPageLiveDiffElement renderiza header con 2 labels, toolbar con BrButton y rowsPane con 4 filas''>\n    <return: #BlScripter>\n    | el scripter |\n    el := self examplePageDiffComputesRows.\n    scripter := BlScripter new element: el.\n    scripter checkStep: [ :s |\n        s label: ''Header has 2 label children''.\n        s value: [ :h | h children size ] equals: [ 2 ].\n        s id: #header ].\n    scripter checkStep: [ :s |\n        s label: ''Toolbar contains a BrButton''.\n        s satisfies: [ :btn | btn isKindOf: BrButton ].\n        s id: #toolbar; / BrButton ].\n    scripter checkStep: [ :s |\n        s label: ''Rows pane has 4 rows''.\n        s value: [ :pane | pane children size ] equals: [ 4 ].\n        s id: #rowsPane ].\n    ^ scripter\n' classified: 'examples'."
			},
			{
				"__type": "textSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"createTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:10:51.689872+01:00"
					}
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:10:51.689872+01:00"
					}
				},
				"paragraphStyle": {
					"__type": "textStyle"
				},
				"string": "**Exploración interactiva**\n\n`buildDiff` construye tres zonas: header, toolbar y rowsPane. Verificamos que `BrHorizontalPane` acepta hijos `BrLabel` y que el conteo de hijos es correcto — la misma estructura que usará `buildDiff` para el header."
			},
			{
				"__type": "pharoSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"code": "| header |\nheader := BrHorizontalPane new hMatchParent; vFitContent.\nheader addChild: (BrLabel new text: 'Repository:').\nheader addChild: (BrLabel new text: 'Working Copy (local):').\nheader children size"
			},
			{
				"__type": "textSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"createTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:10:51.692704+01:00"
					}
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:10:51.692704+01:00"
					}
				},
				"paragraphStyle": {
					"__type": "textStyle"
				},
				"string": "**Implementación mínima**\n\n`buildDiff` construye el `#header` con dos `BrLabel`, el `#toolbar` con un `BrButton` cuya acción llama a `toggleUnchanged`, y el `#rowsPane` que contiene todas las filas. `toggleUnchanged` alterna `showUnchanged` y aplica `BlVisibility gone` / `visible` a las filas `:unchanged`."
			},
			{
				"__type": "pharoSnippet",
				"children": {
					"__type": "snippets",
					"items": []
				},
				"createEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T10:20:56.888662+01:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail": {
					"__type": "email",
					"emailString": "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime": {
					"__type": "time",
					"time": {
						"__type": "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString": "2026-03-23T21:10:51.68775+01:00"
					}
				},
				"uid": {
					"__type": "uid",
					"uidString": "H3ChMpQwQWaqLcJpQ1AB5Q=="
				},
				"code": "LpLtPageLiveDiffElement compile: 'buildDiff\n    | header toolbar rowsPane |\n    diffRows := self computeDiffRows.\n\n    header := BrHorizontalPane new.\n    header id: #header.\n    header hMatchParent; vFitContent.\n    header addChild: (BrLabel new text: ''Repository:'').\n    header addChild: (BrLabel new text: ''Working Copy (local):'').\n\n    toolbar := BrHorizontalPane new.\n    toolbar id: #toolbar.\n    toolbar hMatchParent; vFitContent.\n    toolbar addChild: (BrButton new\n        label: ''Hide unchanged'';\n        action: [ self toggleUnchanged ];\n        yourself).\n\n    rowsPane := BrVerticalPane new.\n    rowsPane id: #rowsPane.\n    rowsPane hMatchParent; vFitContent.\n    diffRows do: [:row | rowsPane addChild: row].\n\n    self layout: BlLinearLayout vertical.\n    self constraintsDo: [:c | c horizontal matchParent. c vertical fitContent].\n    self addChildren: { header. toolbar. rowsPane }.\n    showUnchanged := true\n' classified: 'building'.\n\nLpLtPageLiveDiffElement compile: 'toggleUnchanged\n    showUnchanged := showUnchanged not.\n    diffRows do: [:row |\n        row status = #unchanged ifTrue: [\n            row visibility: (showUnchanged\n                ifTrue: [ BlVisibility visible ]\n                ifFalse: [ BlVisibility gone ]) ] ]\n' classified: 'building'."
			},
